      <p>After initializing the transition probabilities as described above, we iteratively update them using Baum-Welch until convergence to a local optimum of the likelihood. To update α<sub><italic toggle="yes">k</italic></sub>, we compute:<disp-formula><tex-math id="M38">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
